reviewText: Ok so what do you do when you love female-fronted symphonic metal but you live in the states? You order stuff like this to enjoy the visuals and sounds of sweet symphonic metal, cause we all know most of the great female-fronted bands are in Europe and rarely play at the states. This is the latest compilation from ZYX Music with 20 of the latest videos of pure symphonic bands. No need for me to list the videos as it's already listed on Amazon, this is in widescreen with 2.0 surround.
